    "The quantity of providers affects the performance of the collaborative model.",
    "Furthermore, Fig. 7. illustrates the run time.",
    "The number of iterations in different sub-datasets varies depending on the dataset.In summary, the BFLDL approach detects deepfake videos that combine FL, blockchain technology, and DL.",
